# colors: start with hash #rrggbb
#   specify opacity: #rrggbbaa you can compute the
#   aa value by taking the wanted percents of 255 (=FF)
#   eg: 50% = 255/100*50 = 127.499 => int(127.49)=127
#     => hex(127) = 7f; prepend 0 if necessary

